Python Code:

Method 1: Using for Loop
number,sum = 6,0
for i in range(number+1):
  sum+=i
print(sum)
Output:
21

number = 6
sum = int((number * (number + 1))/2)
print(sum)
Output:
21

CPP Code:

Method 1:
#include<iostream>
using namespace std;
int main()
{
    int n=6,sum=0;
    for(int i=1;i<=n;i++)
    {
        sum+=i;
    }
    cout<<sum;
}
output:21

Method 2:
#include<iostream>
using namespace std;
int main()
{
    int n=6,sum=0;
    cout<<n*(n+1)/2;
}
output:21
